products.title: SPOT® EXPLORER
products.description: Spot Explorer is designed for developers eager to explore how flexible mobile robots can be adapted for tasks ranging from industrial inspection to entertainment.

products.title: SPOT® ENTERPRISE
products.description: Spot Enterprise comes equipped with self-charging capabilities and the Spot Dock, allowing it to perform longer inspection tasks and data collection missions with little to no human interaction.

products.title: STRETCH
products.description: Stretch is a versatile mobile robot for case handling, designed for easy deployment in existing warehouses. Unload trucks and build pallets faster by sending the robot to the work, eliminating the need for new fixed infrastructure.

products.title: + ARM
products.description: The Spot Arm enables users to act on data insights and perform physical work in people-centric environments.

products.title: + PORTS

products.title: + INSPECTION
products.description: Spot GXP provides regulated power and an Ethernet port for easy payload integration.

products.title: + THERMAL
products.description: Spot CAM+IR adds a pan-tilt-zoom (PTZ) camera and thermal camera to the Spot CAM to enable detailed inspections.

products.title: + LIDAR
products.description: Spot EAP enhances the range and accuracy of Spot’s autonomy system for use on large sites.

products.title: + EDGE CPU
